+++ b/bfd/ChangeLog
@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@
+2018-09-12  H.J. Lu  <hongjiu.lu@intel.com>
+
+	PR ld/23499
+	* elflink.c (bfd_elf_record_link_assignment): Always clear
